{"tid":190213,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"香港文化係出自港大舍堂","createTime":"2017-04-07T03:33:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T10:37:07.000Z","uid":35870,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"095340e6ebae47617371c0716c2c46b43e574984","tid":190213,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:33:56.000Z","msg":"Case 1<br />\n<br />\nhall膠:<br />\n舍堂文化(包括玩jj，滴蠟)係傳統黎，必須承傳<br />\n<br />\n原居民:<br />\n丁權係傳統權益，基於基本法，必須受到保護<br />\n<br />\nCase 2<br />\n<br />\nhall膠:<br />\n港大舍堂並非宿舍，提供住宿只係bonus(即使大量學生每日要來回三小時返學)<br />\n<br />\n某某golf場:<br />\n提供golf場畀有錢人玩比港人住宿更為重要(即使大量人口住緊劏房)<br />\n<br />\nCase 3<br />\n<br />\n某hall幹事會: fing jj事件不涉及欺凌<br />\n<br />\n保良局: 訓練營不涉及欺凌行為<br />\n<br />\nCase 4<br />\n<br />\nhall膠們一致認同拍片個位無問題，係爆條片出黎個個先有問題<br />\n<br />\n藍絲認為政府政策無問題，係民主派經常雞蛋裏挑骨頭，係撕裂社會元兇<br />\n<br />\nCase 5<br />\n<br />\n大仙們指出:我地非常民主，歡迎任何人提出意見，但所有改革應該遵從由大仙老鬼定落黎嘅舍堂傳統<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥指出: 歡迎市民討論政改方案，但任何政改方案必須沿用人大常委會定落黎嘅831框架<br />\n<br />\nCase 6<br />\n<br />\n入hall前大仙:我地間hall好開心，快d join我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQuit hall 後:(係u street見到)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />-&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />-&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(西面走左)<br />\n<br />\n入教會前:歡迎弟兄join我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n離教後: 咦佢自殺喎，報警先<br />\n<br />\nCase 7<br />\n<br />\nhall膠: 我覺得大仙屌我個陣我真係獲益良多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，成個人進步左！咦，又係時候要請大仙食勁過飯(註:勁過飯係考試前<span style=\"color: pink;\">被逼</span>一齊食飯，意指祝願大家gpa過3，好似係)<br />\n<br />\n人生課程學員: 我覺得呀keith嘅指導改變左我成個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝你呀keith！咦，係時候要交學費<br />\n<br />\nCase 8<br />\n<br />\n人生課程導師: 不涉及洗腦<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦: 我地d hall 絕對唔係個d人生課程啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(註:出自某港大講座:舍堂令大學生離地?<br />\n有興趣者可search youtube)"},{"pid":"e90b02ded83dc403788af13dd4d6d021b9b3a1cd","tid":190213,"uid":14799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:44:45.000Z","msg":"Aggeer💯"},{"pid":"357a3b3888764407185c429c93d7e60f4a3c3fc2","tid":190213,"uid":91645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:08:42.000Z","msg":"咩比喻嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c432481051abe34c1d0bbeec410773a1e60f2778","tid":190213,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65055b58bff74ce865801203be67c48c3d276ed3","tid":190213,"uid":24469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:22:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c30c29fef3c1ef5520bbd9189b4f54fe6039a9d","tid":190213,"uid":10171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:24:43.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有香港既三性家奴文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n英國中國邊個做主人都冇所謂，只要主人話咩就要做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"